content: I'm trying to plan out my day and need some help with time management. Can you help me figure out the best way to fit in a 30-minute workout session during the week, considering my lunch break is at 12:30 PM and I usually take a short break at 2:00 PM? By the way, I've been getting up at 6:30 AM consistently for my new job, which has been a big change for me.
